posts.description:
Happy earth day everyone!! Back at a blogger retreat I attended a few weeks ago, a few of us got to chatting about the importance of our National Park system, and so @sasha.swerdloff and I decided to put together a blogger "virtual hike" on Earth Day (that's today!) through some of the park systems near each of us. I’ve @-mentioned everyone who participated below, (highly recommend taking a look at all the incredible and different national parks everyone visited! So beautiful.) Our national park system is a treasure and I hope it will be around for future generations. I’m sharing a travel guide for Olympic National Park up on the blog today, and you can take a peek at it at AdventuresInCooking.com 💚🌿💚 #ourwild #livefolk 
